{"tid":1157271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[McCafe送免費指定飲品!] 毋須消費即可獲贈McCafe指定飲品一杯","createTime":"2019-05-16T07:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:51:42.000Z","uid":240656,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ceac198d918d912f09b3d66cd64237efa99f4839","tid":1157271,"uid":240656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qr.hkfood.review/2019/05/mccafe-free-drink.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqr.hkfood.review%2F2019%2F05%2Fmccafe-free-drink.html&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=40954183\" target=\"_blank\">https://qr.hkfood.review/2019/05/mccafe-free-drink.html</a><br />\nMcCafe全新推出芝士奶蓋系列飲品，同時今年係McCafe 20週年喇!<br />\n<br />\n慶祝McCafe 20週年，由即日起McCafe會於銅鑼灣希慎廣場、麥當勞App和「麥麥送」免費送出20萬杯芝士奶蓋飲品！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>麥當勞App毋須消費即可獲贈McCafe指定飲品一杯</strong><br />\n於麥當勞App送出飲品優惠券，憑App內優惠券可以於5月16日至5月22日1400 - 0000期間(及McCafe營業時間內)到McCafe分店換領一杯大杯裝「芝士奶蓋黑咖啡」或「芝士奶蓋四季春」飲品。<br />\n<em>(不適用於機場分店)</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>麥當勞App McCafe指定飲品買一送一</strong><br />\n於麥當勞App提供兩張買一送一優惠券。憑每張優惠券購買一杯大杯裝的芝士奶蓋飲品，即可免費獲贈一杯相同價格或以下的大杯裝芝士奶蓋飲品。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>希慎廣場Pop-up Store免費派發飲品</strong><br />\nMcCafe由5月16日起至5月19日於銅鑼灣希慎廣場設立期問限定Pop-up Store，於指定時段會以先到先得形式免費派發指定口味的芝士奶蓋飲品。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>麥麥送消費滿HK$100即送一杯芝士奶蓋</strong><br />\n凡於「麥麥送」單次消費滿HK$100，即可免費獲贈一杯芝士奶蓋系列飲品。"},{"pid":"a55d7a86f9a474356bbf824a078b1fb2ad5950ce","tid":1157271,"uid":240656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3540bc5a5e3aa67cefaa559bc7a3a06d6b63f4","tid":1157271,"uid":886,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFiFf5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFiFf5u.png&h=27b88047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入左貨先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得紫菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82676b072c24addd35c318bb424186edf420e9e6","tid":1157271,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"換咗 幾好飲"},{"pid":"704db394641b301e40e9e9a121ac56e3a2744855","tid":1157271,"uid":36465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:41:37.000Z","msg":"派左？ 打開個麥當勞app唔見有優惠券"},{"pid":"9f7c3f704f3df471fc9041028af5251b204e6082","tid":1157271,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b663e3dd555531efaf548f5c43d5923e72ce560","tid":1157271,"uid":36465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f7c3f704f3df471fc9041028af5251b204e6082","tid":1157271,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"704db394641b301e40e9e9a121ac56e3a2744855","tid":1157271,"uid":36465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:41:37.000Z","msg":"派左？ 打開個麥當勞app唔見有優惠券"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"ic 屋企公司附近都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2452edd983e5c51d090f92ef33f9ba38c4a7dafb","tid":1157271,"uid":159168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82676b072c24addd35c318bb424186edf420e9e6","tid":1157271,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"換咗 幾好飲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"認真?"},{"pid